title: Wow Wow Wubbzy - Wubbzy Goes BOO! - DVDRip
description:
Watch as Wubbzy, Widget, Walden and Daizy try to collect the very last leaf of autumn, pick the perfect pumpkin and create the spookiest Halloween costume of all!  There's singing, dancing, trick or treating, and kickity-kick ball too, plus plenty of positive values like creativity, patience and responsibility.  It's all here and it's so much fun it's scary!

140 minute runtime
